data.text:
Graham Media Group is THE authentic, accessible, local voice passionately informing and celebrating our communities. 

WKMG News 6 is one of the foremost television stations in the Central Florida area. Serving nine counties, WKMG News 6 provides award-winning daily-newscasts, in-depth investigations, local entertainment and network programming to the community. News 6 has received numerous accolades for their work including the prestigious Edward R. Murrow Award and multiple Emmy and Associated Press awards.
